\frac{a}{b}\cdot\frac{c}{d}=\frac{ac}{bd}
(a^b)\cdot (a^c)=a^{b+c}
x = \dfrac ab, \; y = \dfrac cd
xy = \dfrac ab \cdot \dfrac cd = \dfrac {a\cdot c}{b \cdot d}.
